<!id: eclipse-api-deprecations>
<!description: Replace deprecated Eclipse Platform API calls with modern alternatives.
Covers patterns found in Eclipse Platform 2025 commits.>
<!severity: warning>
<!tags: eclipse, deprecation, migration>

// Platform.run → SafeRunner.run (deprecated in Eclipse 4.x)
org.eclipse.core.runtime.Platform.run($runnable)
=> org.eclipse.core.runtime.SafeRunner.run($runnable)
;;
